Description:
You arrive at some ruins where the soil seems very fertile and many exotic plants that you have never seen before are growing in it.

Walking through the garden you find some berries that seem edible but what catches your attention is a large tree.

As you approach, you see that in front of the tree is a wolf, munching joyfully on a golden apple that shines brightly.
